'''Gurijoog''' ([[ingiriis]]: domestic livestock) waa [[xayawaan]]ka iyo [[xoolo|xoolaha]] la dhaqdo ee [[dad]]ku manaafacaadsado.

Xoolaha gurijoogta ah waxaa ka mid ah [[bisad]]aha, [[ey]]da, [[lo']]da, [[adhi]]ga, [[daanyeer]]ka, [[geel]]a, [[faras|fardaha]], [[dameer]]aha, [[ido|idaha]] iyo mararka qaar oo lagu daro [[digaag]]a iyo [[shimbir]]aha kale la dhaqdo.

Guud ahaan xoolaha gurijoogta ah waa xayawaanka aadamuhu
dhaqdaan, ee qaarkood la cuno [[hilib]]kooda lana cabo [[Caano|caanahooda]].

[[Xayawaan]]ka aan la dhaqanin ee khatarta ah waxaa loo yaqaanaa [[Duurjoog]], waxaana ka mid [[libaax]]a, [[waraabe|waraabaha]], [[shabeel]]ka, [[harimacad]]ka, [[yey]]ga, [[buti]]da, [[mas]]aska, iyo kuwo kale oo badan.


